       </para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
       <para>
        Remove psql warning when connecting to an older server (Peter Eisentraut)
       </para>

       <para>
        The warning when connecting to a newer server was retained.
       </para>
      </listitem>

     </itemizedlist>

    <sect5>
     <title>Backslash Commands</title>

     <itemizedlist>

      <listitem>
       <para>
